data.description: MUSTANG has a NEW LISTING, come check it out before it's gone! Sought after neighborhood, in Top Rated Mustang School District, it's close to Parks, Shopping, Restaurants, Hospitals, and so much more.  This solid Brick home has Updates,  Painted Inside and out, Roof 2022,  Wood looking Porcelain Tile, and more.  Enjoy your a big Open Living and Dining rooms, 10ft ceilings, lots of windows, Fireplace. Primary is very big with big walkin closet, Whirlpool tub, double vanity, separate shower. There's a Huge Study/ 2nd Livingroom, that can be a Bedrm 4, workout rm, kids room, hobby room, you decide!  Surround Sound.  Has Sprinkler system, but it's sold as it. Covered Porch and Huge Covered Patio. Wood fence in backyard, Out Bldg for lawnmower, bikes, etc.  Buyers to verify schools.
